+.Sh RETURN VALUES
+The
+.Nm
+utility exits with one of the following values:
+.Bl -tag -width Ds
+.It 0
+One or more processes were matched.
+.It 1
+No processes were matched.
+.It 64 (EX_USAGE)
+Invalid command-line options were specified.
+.El
 .Sh HISTORY
